record.title: PRIVILEGES OF THE FLOOR
record.narrative:
PRIVILEGES OF THE FLOOR -- (Senate - July 26, 2007)

[Page: S10208]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, I ask unanimous consent that Jeffrey Watters, a fellow in Senator Cantwell's office, be given floor privileges for the duration of the consideration of this bill.

record.chair: Without objection, it is so ordered.
